Using Latex, complete the following sentence: A \underline{\hspace{1cm}} is a mathematical function that transforms a set of inputs into a corresponding set of outputs.
Rewrite prompt as a question: Can you fill in the blank to complete the following sentence using Latex: A \underline{\hspace{1cm}} is a mathematical function that transforms a set of inputs into a corresponding set of outputs?

Certainly! To complete the sentence in LaTeX, you can fill in the blank with a suitable word. Here's how you might do it:

```latex
A \underline{\text{function}} is a mathematical function that transforms a set of inputs into a corresponding set of outputs.
```

This will underline the word "function" in the sentence.
